## Attribution
All sounds are CC0 1.0 Universal (Public Domain Dedication). No attribution required.

## Known quality flags for Auditor
1. death_sting: 8-bit retro style (Fupicat/538151) — aesthetic mismatch with folk-horror register. Works functionally. Recommend replacing with a darker sting if a matching CC0 source is found.
2. cave_ambient: ~8 sec loop — may produce audible seam on repeat. Short but the engine's `src.loop=true` handles it.
3. eldritch_ambient: ~10 sec loop — same seam concern. szegvari's dark fantasy work is aesthetically correct.
4. boss_intro_drone: "Inception.mp3" title suggests BRAAAM — cinematic but effective for boss intro.
5. boss:intro, dialog:open, ui:reveal, torch:active events are stubbed in EVENT_MAP — wired and ready, but engine must emit these events to activate. See wg-audio.js:61-65.

## Freesound search behavior note
freesound.org search does NOT work via Chrome MCP (returns 0 results — JavaScript-rendered results). Server-side HTML search via curl DOES work. All searches done via curl + HTTP HEAD for file size verification.
